issue.title: Back-end planning
issue.body: Backend will be written in Node.js and will interface with http://www.openstreetmap.org/ API. Possible sources of data include: https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1bKm78yhnQE28_QKbI10Z5j0qtM8 and http://dmwilson.info/Home/Search . Plan back-end below.
